Package pl.edu.agh.kis.pz1.player

Class Tie

java.lang.Object
pl.edu.agh.kis.pz1.player.Tie
public class Tie extends Object
Tie is the static class that breaks the tie. It may settle when both players have:
  • straight flush
  • four of a kind
  • full house
  • flush
  • straight
  • free of a kind
  • two pair
  • one pair
  • high card
